{
  "texts": [
    "Children are living in a world dramatically transformed by emerging AI/ML systems.",
    "Moreover, their everyday life is transformed by numerous crises, pandemic, on-going wars and climate change as notable examples.",
    "All this is causing anxiety, sorrow and fear among children, concerning their future as well as the future of the globe and humankind.",
    "Now, more than ever, we need to engage children as changemakers for a better -more equal, just, sustainable -future.",
    "Computing education, on its part, should foster children's agency regarding their (digitalized) futures."
  ]
}